article.description: — Storm Murphy had 23 points and 11 assists as Wofford defeated Samford 94-84 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Murphy scores 23 to lift Wofford over Samford 94-84
article.linkText: Murphy scores 23 to lift Wofford over Samford 94-84
article.story: SPARTANBURG, S.C. -- — Storm Murphy had 23 points and 11 assists as Wofford defeated Samford 94-84 on Saturday night. B.J. Mack had 15 points for Wofford (5-3, 2-0 Southern Conference), which earned its fourth straight home victory. Tray Hollowell added 15 points. Morgan Safford had 14 points. Jacob Tryon had 19 points for the Bulldogs (5-4, 1-1). Myron Gordon added 16 points. A.J. Staton-McCray had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
